
= Video series in which [[Hazel Henderson]] interviews economic and social changemakers.

URL = http://ffh.films.com/id/20385/Ethical_Markets_3_Transforming_Finance.htm

=Description=

"What is the purpose of finance in human societies, and what principles should guide investing and trade? Can definitions of wealth be expanded to include clean air and water, and the quality of daily life? In this nine-part series scholar and producer Hazel Henderson interviews key figures in the ethical economics movement. Each program identifies ways to bring financial practices into alignment with social values, helping to create an environmentally sustainable future. 9-part series, 29 minutes each."


